                         java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> t,
                         int points)
Constructor for TestResultDetails that contains a path to the html file

Parameters:
output - indicates the number of failed tests, if 0 then the test passed if -1 then the test was skipped
name - indicates the test name of the the test case
desc - indicates the synopsis line from the test
warning - indicates any warning messages - only set with skipped tests
plot_path - indicates the path to the plot file
html_path - indicates teh path to the html file
c - vector of component tags associated with test
t - vector of test tags associated with test
points - is the number of variables multiplied by the number os steps
